## Install

```sh
# via pnpm
pnpm add @goodnight-dev/{{dashCase pkg}}
# or via npm
npm install @goodnight-dev/{{dashCase pkg}}
```

The same utilities are available through the umbrella package, if you'd rather
depend on one thing:

```ts
import {} from '@goodnight-dev/utils/{{dashCase pkg}}';
import {} from '@goodnight-dev/utils';
```

